snippet: The attack was the deadliest single attack on the international force in Sudan.
abstract: United Nations peacekeeping team is ambushed by gunmen in Darfur, Sudan; no group has claimed responsibility for attack, which left 7 dead and 17 wounded.
lead_paragraph: The attack was the deadliest single attack on the international force in Sudan.

headline.main: Darfur Attack Kills 7 in Force Sent to Sudan By the U.N.
headline.print_headline: Darfur Attack Kills 7 in Force Sent to Sudan By the U.N.
